text: KWSO (91.9 FM, "Warm Springs Radio") is a radio station broadcasting a Hot Adult Contemporary music format. Licensed to Warm Springs, Oregon, United States, the station is currently owned by Confederated Tribes Warm Springs Reservation. Historically, KWSO was an AM station in Wasco, CA, operating on 1050 kHz (1950's and 60's). ==See also== *List of community radio stations in the United States ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Native American radio WSO Category:Hot adult contemporary radio stations in the United States Category:Jefferson County, Oregon Category:NPR member stations Category:Community radio stations in the United States
